      description: 'Identify the cause of damp, mould or timber decay—especially important for properties on exposed plots or with historic alterations.',
    },
    {
      name: 'Ventilation & Indoor Air Quality Review',
      description: 'Assess airflow and extractor performance to keep homes comfortable and free from condensation.',
    },
    {
      name: 'Measured Surveys & Planning Support',
      description: 'Precise drawings and feasibility advice for extensions, conversions or planning submissions across Dobshill.',
    },
  ],
};

const localInsights = {
  heading: `What to watch for in ${townName} homes`,
  paragraphs: [
    'Former Ministry of Defence land and reclaimed sites can feature made ground or varying foundation depths. We review cracks, drainage runs and garden levels to assess stability.',
    'Many Dobshill houses have dormer loft conversions or reconfigured ground floors. We inspect structural supports, insulation and fire protection so you understand any follow-up actions.',
    'Exposure on the hill means wind-driven rain can affect brickwork, render and roof detailing. We highlight maintenance priorities for soffits, gutters and pointing to avoid damp ingress.',
  ],
};

const additionalInsights = [
  {
    heading: 'Planning, renovation and future works',
    paragraphs: [
      `${townName} homeowners often explore additional living space, from kitchen extensions to garden offices. We outline structural considerations, permissions and realistic phasing to keep projects compliant.`,
      'We provide balanced advice on damp treatment, ventilation upgrades and energy improvements so investment delivers comfort without creating new moisture risks.',
    ],
  },
  {
    heading: 'Aftercare and client support',
    paragraphs: [
      'You remain in direct contact with Liam before and after the survey. We review follow-up photos, clarify report items for solicitors and help you prioritise works so decisions are well informed.',
    ],
  },
